Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂啊  到底算不算有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,前提的世界觀說明太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全讀不進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師這不是能好好地評價麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子君  前提的世界觀說明太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不光是台詞  解說也太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,試試看憋氣從最初開始讀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀到哪兒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一頁都沒有讀完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀者能讀得下去的只有一口氣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是沒法抓住讀者的眼球  讀者就會直接略過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在發表正經的評論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是說得一針見血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實在這個Jumpo的人氣作品中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.13,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自周刊少年Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一口氣能看完一整話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.22,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：這裡大概是指的久保帶人的漫畫「死神」喜歡畫整頁和特寫分鏡的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概不是指這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總之你的漫畫在抓住對方眼球之前就已經憋死上百次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,練得可以憋氣三分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,延長憋氣時間又是什麼操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我放這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:36.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:39.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在這兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我沒事哦  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼變成這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.10,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}佳作  夏日死屍  45P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.10,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}短島佩佩（21歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十…丸…院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是寄到工作室會妨礙到您的作畫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是我的英明的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼英明的判斷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,寄到家裡來要是被姬發現了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是姬被來路不明的應募作品給壓到了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,複印起來也很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用PDF文件發過來也行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您還知道PDF文件的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:17.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過這應募作品的量還真是驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在如今還能收到這麼多的應募作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看來這個行業看來還沒有步入夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一箱子一冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用的亞馬遜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十…丸…院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不是照您說的寄到工作室了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說過的是把PDF文件發到工作室裡的電腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作室？PDF?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請不要一次說兩件事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:03.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不是聖德太子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不妙啊  十丸院…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙真的不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,趕緊讀了進行評價吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  難得這麼多女孩子登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,臉卻沒有畫得易於分辨…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:26.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明節奏挺好的  在這兒強行加入黃段子真的有必要麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部不都在說我自己麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.82,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,907.8,80,-45)}輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.24,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,975.8,80,-45.4)}輪不到你說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.62,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977.6,80,-59.8)}後藤還敢說這種話哦w
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.99,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,-60)}這傢伙扔出好大個迴旋鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.07,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,80)}你這立場還敢這麼說的麼w
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.07,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,250)}輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.07,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,430)}輪不到你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.07,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,600)}那你來畫啊你來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.07,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\move(80,977,80,780)}這話能由你講？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是寫了這種評價的話就會成「輪不到你說」大遊行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了  這兒就朝著模稜兩可的方向寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.08,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frx14\fry0\frz18.77\org(377.6,288)\pos(265.6,270.4)\c&H606165&}講評  第95回  漫畫人  新人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:36.79,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}他人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行  這關係到他人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就跟履歷書一樣的  不是能胡來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.96,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H4E4E62&\frz297.5\pos(1384,360)}不採用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,的確很有壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟可能關係到他人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟這些畫漫畫的人  也都是誰家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是姬的作品得到了不合理的評價大概也會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.36,kakushigoto in 4 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\move(1009.6,85.8,737.6,139.2)}完全不行獎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.36,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz270.1\c&H6A6575&\move(879.2,254,670.4,284.8)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.36,kakushigoto in 4 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\move(1038.2,841.4,792,716.8)}後藤姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.11,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an6}怒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把應募作品都當做是小姬畫的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不僅僅是給予鼓勵  要為了讓其成長而指出缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就能給出溫柔一點的建議了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.75,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\frz24.99\c&H89909F&\pos(545.6,742.4)}呀  變態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬不會畫這種漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,家…家長倒是在畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖說是我輪班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這樣的工作我還以為是屬於底層人員的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.14,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\bord5\c&HF3F29C&\3c&HC466EE&\pos(299.2,768)}底層人員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.65,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,92.8)}拿報紙  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.65,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1267.6,131.6)}鎖門  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.65,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1296.4,826)}收拾  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師寫的新人獎的評語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太過嚴肅對搞笑漫畫家來說真生硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣就很柔和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說不定是個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.79,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}周刊少年  漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.79,kakushigoto in 7 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\c&HA75CDE&\frz271.2\pos(688.667,718)}在閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.87,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(1854,64,2000,64)}首先  得取一個更加能吸引讀者眼球的標題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.87,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(1802,66,1960,66)}搞不懂是什麼樣的漫畫（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(1480,62,1886,62,0,4000)}劇情的高潮有兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(1428,62,1820,62,0,4000)}登場人物太多了以至於每個角色的印象都不鮮明（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(966,32,1385,32,0,4000)}我認為從中挑出一個角色進行深度的角色塑造更好（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(638,20,1038,20,0,4000)}以童話為基礎的殘酷故事類如今是個競爭非常激烈的類別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(586,20,980,20,0,4000)}而這位作者能畫出很可愛的女孩子（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(170,60,580,60,0,4000)}同樣是童話的話  也想看像「紅髮安妮」那樣能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:12.51,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&HFBF6F1&\frz270\move(118,60,530,60,0,4000)}開心地讀下去的故事（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師太胡來了以至於在網絡上被罵慘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可真是讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十…丸…院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可沒寫上什麼括弧笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明我都忍住沒有寫得模稜兩可而是認真的去寫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣不僅不有趣  而且還像是在故意搗亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這原來不是老師加上的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不妙啊…那傢伙真的不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難得我接下了評委這種討厭的輪班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這對待是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也接了不喜歡的輪班  彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼哦  不喜歡的輪班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師你自身就是輪班制的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:57.34,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\c&H3E415A&\3c&HB9B4C4&\pos(801,66.4)}後藤班負責會議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下一個後藤班是我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,討厭的輪班要是沒人去做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,業界是運轉不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你來做囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明回中學館就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.01,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自日本綜合出版社小學館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我原來是需要輪班制的麻煩漫畫家麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為  確實很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸在公司裡也有值日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是現在最重要的輪班是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把姬給好好撫養長大這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟爸爸也是被人撫養長大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一天也會輪到姬來輪班撫養人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我會儘早輪班的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…不用那麼急也可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,二十年後  甚至更晚些都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:34.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在就做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,撫養狗狗的輪班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣的話得先做許多功課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對撫養的輪班來說做功課很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也做過功課麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:48.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後  現在也有幸在做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.99,kakushigoto in 4 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(985.6,131.2)}爸爸  值日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.99,kakushigoto in 4 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1656,136)}姬  休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去趟便利店就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.37,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\frz270\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H040404&\pos(716.8,334.4)}草莓  巧克力撬棍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.37,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自日本食品企業森永制果的經典零食大嘴鳥巧克力球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作提前結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我買來了姬喜歡的零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個很好吃我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟姬一直都在吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:25.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:32.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是  抱歉爸爸突然來工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,上班族真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.03,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1067.2,592)\frz332.8}住下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.03,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自河合克敏漫畫「鈴裡高校書道部」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能說明一下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終審沒能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終審是指由編輯部進行的最終檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確認內容以及表達  偶爾會出現這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用下流段子經常有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:04.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根據編輯方案  重畫後半八頁就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,期限是早上五點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:07.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早上五點？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼想都不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,印刷廠似乎只能等到這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的在完成前讓他們等著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,時代變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在漫畫雜誌到處都在減少的如今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對印刷廠來說第一重要的客戶並不是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個夕陽產業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你不也是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那且不說  現在排第一的是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:39.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,零食的包裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個很好吃我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我準備了能讓您集中注意力的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,閉關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也想來這麼一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也想這麼關一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,夕陽產業用的經費也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  我和這裡的老闆是熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這傢伙應該是走後門進來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:21.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要是通宵閉關的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬就很寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您要是在家裡畫可是會被姬發現的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:30.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,六點鐘前有納德拉小姐在還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這之後我好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去替您守著姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請老師您放心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:48.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是志治君嗎  睡了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可惡  沒有一個人接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作才剛結束這也不怪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你為什麼在洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有  你來多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,回家的途中我遇見了十丸院先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他給我了酒店的房卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去了一趟工作室把工具都拿了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但穿著這一身  我實在是畫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你換成浴袍就能畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為這樣感覺很放鬆嘛  但你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒必要也穿著浴袍畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不挺好的嘛  這可是今治浴袍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.21,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：今治是日本四國地區的一個知名品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過  這樣兩個人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就像是密會一樣  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:44.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果讓周刊雜誌拍到這樣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.2\fs70\bord3\c&H544F50&\move(6.4,273.6,78,292)}抓拍到整夜在市內高級旅館密會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\c&H5A5758&\3c&HF9F9F9&\frz293.8\move(1492.8,320,1396.6,372)}黃段子漫畫家在現實生活中也同樣全力搞黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H929193&\frz21.64\move(153.6,763.2,187,771)}漫畫家GK（右邊）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H929193&\frz21.21\move(504,627.2,499.2,651.2)}助手SR（左邊）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這將成為我對助手出手的醜聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後被世間廣泛傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就會被姬嫌棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.73,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\pos(360,273.6)}自我意識過剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快來個人啊  不管是誰來個男性工作人員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的電話錄音我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼事啊  把我叫到賓館來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你來得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:08.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道  老師要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我雖然很想出道但是這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不是可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說你是後藤老師的責編？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:35.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師拜託我來照看姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哦…那辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬小姐  那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不能跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要完成和老師的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像  有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.00,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893.6,66.6)}靈異特集
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:11.18,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H0F00B1&\3c&H040404&\frz9.622\pos(220.8,299.2)}我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:11.18,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord2\c&H960003&\pos(1712,937.6)}座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一名童女的靈魂在正中間漂浮著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這正是座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.22,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}叮咚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.43,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}驚嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您能為我們家帶來繁榮興盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還請住下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.90,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日本傳說中座敷童子能為家族帶來繁盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我和父母吵架後離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不能吵架呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  只有姬你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸因為突然來了工作所以出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊  所以才說父親都不靠譜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看來我必須得住下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用害怕了哦  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢  酷酷的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來的服務時間能拜託您延長到明天早晨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行  我還有下一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  下一位客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要取消嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我又回來了  姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好擔心啊  好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她都已經十歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您擔心過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你別說這些不負責任的話  還有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼連你也穿著浴袍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就我一個人沒穿不很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在姬肯定獨自一個人  很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是奈留的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你幾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像不能問偶像年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你幾歲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:53.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我17歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,外邊有人在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一定是…我的跟蹤狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.50,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\pos(347.2,651.2)\c&H52525E&}自我意識過剩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:11.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偶像肯定會有跟蹤狂  這就是偶像的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,奇怪的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是跟蹤狂放的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,裡面好像是金屬罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣很危險的  納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我曾在我的國家看到過和這個類似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用日語講
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是炸彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺裡邊好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:38.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:38.99,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日語中兩個詞相近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,周刊漫畫的編輯怎麼可能像你一樣這麼閒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可和這家人是熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,問一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有人認識這個流氓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,跟蹤狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你到底是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就當我是個多才多藝的明星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼不早點告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡有浴袍party
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可不是浴袍party
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這讓我對老師另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然這麼適合浴袍打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654.4,206.4)}石破茂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(657.6,249.6)}註：日本眾議院議員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(745.6,356.8)}館博
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,403.2)}註：日本演員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,596.8)}後藤可久士  {\c&H6046EF&\bord2\blur5\3c&HC466EE&\3a&H73&}NEW！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748.8,694.4)}田村正和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.99,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(753.6,742.4)}註：日本演員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,帥到排在館博後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這算稱讚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別  別管這些了  趕快工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼不告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還好趕上了這場浴袍party
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你沒趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有這不是浴袍party
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,通宵真是好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再見  姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好了  趕快走  流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都說了我是超級多才多藝明星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這樣子是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有些沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是太寂寞了才沒有睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.92,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日語中閉關和罐頭同音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,傳說中的罐頭真的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我給你看證據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這其中肯定搞錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:29.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,玩具罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.86,kakushigoto in 4 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(510.4,52.8)}中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.86,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(404.8,376)\frz1.633}金色1枚  銀色5枚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.86,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\frz2.266\pos(505.6,564.8)\c&H464C5D&}快來收集鳥喙印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才吃這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是喜歡裡面的巧克力才吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:44.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我已經得到金了  不用再買了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都吃了  你真的很喜歡吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我再買很多回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的  真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.88,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\pos(849.6,84.8)}吃了的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼拿了銀牌的人會哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因為得集滿5枚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當你得到金的時候很開心對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但得到銀的時候也很開心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:16.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是我在學校裡做的金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個送給爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:34.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然這很老套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但當我真的得到的時候  真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  這是什麼的金牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:43.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對我來說  爸爸就是我的金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:51.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等到姬長大有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就會變為銀牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在寫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了不讓我忘記今天我拿到了金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:13.45,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.29\pos(972.8,739.2)}金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使以後成為了銀  我也能夠忍受住痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然還是金的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:20.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是金哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我找到了媽媽留下來的箱子的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很是高興  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這異樣的感覺究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然  這是爸爸的字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:53.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,箱子的後續  是爸爸留下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:58.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
